column5: I just had the best time  again this year and really enjoyed meeting and re-meeting all of you fine folks. Here are a few pics of the 2007 OFC Lakair G2G. Should anyone want high res. copies, let me know and I'll email you what you want.
Here are a few more:
Thanks Roy, they turned out great !!  I've been waiting for someone to post a pic of the group shot for my album.
great photos thanks for sharing
And a few more:
You got some great shots Roy!  They turned out GREAT!  If you could send me the full size Group shot I wold appreciate it.  Maureen

I have a few more but, what happens at Lakair STAYS at Lakair. I also have 4-5 other group shots which might be a little clearer. Just give me a sign if you want any of these pics in high res (there's a BIG difference)
DAMN Satans time zone!!!... I missed the fricken group shot!!!  Shoot me a high res shot please sir!!!
Next year ... bring a big wooly coat and you can come out of the cabin.
Hello Roy. Great pictures! I would like a high res group shot as well please. Thank you!
Great pics Roy! Thanks for sharing with us!
That's what I call Pics!  Geez the camera musta been runnin' hot man! Gotta like those late nite shots!  All the guys looked kinda wazzoodled!
looks like you all had a blast.
Great shots Roy.  Next year I'll be there.  TJ and Chris...cleaning the pike with no board underneath...I'm impressed.

Great shots Roy!  The before and after shots of Chris and TJ in the fish cleaning house are priceless and can be blamed Glen I suppose?  Pics of Wayne and Leah, looks like they were enjoying themselves.  Good pic of Chris's boat at the dock, it's is a awesome ride.  Where was Art trying to take his boat? hillclimbing?  Glad to see most of the pictures of you in the upright position, you must have rested up for this years gala event.   Thanks for sharing!  Whopper
Thats a great collection you got yerself my friend. TSF
Can I get one of the geezer sleeping in the chair? It reminds me of me!
Which geezer, Paul? There are a few of them.
Roy..thanks for posting all those pics!  We've saved them all on our computer.  We have a few shots, but realized that there were a few people we never did get in a picture.
Great pics Roy. Thanks for posting them.
LOL Roy great shots of a great group!
Great pics, added a few more to my album
Great pic's Roy.... I'm still working on mine...
Nice pics Roy.  Looks like everyone had a great time!  I hope I can make it next year.  Aaron
Thanks. You'd better make it there next year Aaron or I'll come and get ya.
